                  <summary><p>A multi-text manuscript, entitled <title xml:lang="ta">Vētāntam 2</title> on its additional title page, containing two <term xml:lang="sa">Vedānta</term> works:
  <list rend="numbered">
    <item>the <title xml:lang="ta">Kolai Maṟuttal</title>, by <persName role="author">Cāntaliṅka Tēcikar</persName>. 22 stanzas. See Zvelebil (1995, p. 119).</item>
    <item>the <title xml:lang="ta">Ñāṉavāciṭṭam</title> by <persName role="author">Aḷavantār Māṭavappaṭṭar</persName>. 43/44 <foreign xml:lang="ta">katai</foreign>s. 2054 stanzas. See Zvelebil (1995, p. 26).</item>
  </list>
  </p>
<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (November 2021).</p>
<p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p> 
